channel.title: How do I make tab/emote teleports?
channel.description:
Well, I'm using Reapage-Scape source, and it had all of these teleports, and my friend deleted them, but he's in Florida and I can't ask him how.
Anyway, I have one teleport left, Home. And i was wondering how would I make it so if I click on the tab next to hime (ie.) it would bring me to my train area?
If anyone could help me out, that'd be great,
And I also need to know [b]where to put it[/b], and if I need any extra things to it.
Thanks!
~ Me ~
